data.description:
Absolutely Stunning! Custom built CYPRESS exterior home with lots of upgrades too numerous to list.
 Located in the East Central School District In (Hurley) Moss Point Mississippi and Big Point community. Only one minute from the Golf course, 18 Miles from Mobile Regional airport. 29 minutes to Ingalls Shipbuilding.  The property begins with a long driveway entrance nestled amidst beautiful lined trees embracing nature's awesomeness unveiling its picturesque surroundings of this exquisite home. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail beginning with the beautiful front covered entrance. Step inside to the open floor plan, high ceilings, custom plantation shutters,  hand-scraped engineered hardwood flooring throughout to include a formal dining room, breakfast nook, living room area with a gas log fireplace with custom River Rock masonry, the custom built in bookshelf with rolling ladder. From the inviting living areas adorned with rustic accents to the gourmet chef's kitchen boasting top-of-the-line Viking Professional Stainless Steel appliances and custom soft-close cabinetry, commercial vent hood, dual ovens, wine cooler, wine storage rack, and the bar area decorated with River Rock masonry revealing every aspect of this home has been thoughtfully curated for both comfort and style. 

Retreat to the lavish Primary suite, where tranquility reigns. Pamper yourself in the spa-like ensuite bath, complete with luxurious amenities and a soaking tub for ultimate relaxation. Each bedroom has its own private ensuite bathroom.

The  32 X 23 detached Garage/workshop is climate controlled, has a full bathroom with a walk-in shower, washer/dryer hookups, hot water heater and attic storage.  The previous owner lived here while building.  Can be easily converted to a mother N law  suite.
Has (2) 50 AMP RV hookups (detached garage &  exterior of house)

Outside, a private oasis awaits, featuring an outdoor kitchen and entertaining area, a covered screened patio perfect for hosting gatherings or simply basking in the beauty of nature. With ample space for a pool the possibilities for creating your dream outdoor sanctuary are endless.
